title: #92Noon! JG/Birk/Siny/Lavelle/PJ
description: Hear from Justin Gaard in the first hour, and HC PJ Fleck to end the show on the Gophers following their season opener on Sunday. Matt Birk and Dave Sinykin both offer football opinions, baseball and pigskin with Lavelle final hour as well!
